             was indicted for <rs id="t17820410-70-off367" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17820410-70-off367" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820410-70-off367" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17820410-70-cd368" type="crimeDate">25th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820410-70-off367 t17820410-70-cd368"></join> last, one black sattin cloak, value 8 s. a linen apron, value 6 d. a check shirt, and two linen shirts
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17820410-70-victim852" type="victimName">
                     Christopher 
                     Holder
                  <interp inst="t17820410-70-victim852" type="surname" value="Holder"></interp>
